# Codes API
Codes API is a service for *IBGE*, brazilian statistics institution service, providing access to location's codes based on descriptions.

# Group Codes
Codes related resources of the **Codes API**.

## Note [/code/{nome_municipio}]
A single Code object with all its details.

+ Parameters
    + nome_municipio (required, string, `Sao Paulo`) ... City name is listed on IBGE data as `nome_municipio`, The spelling of the city name must be exact. Returns the most likely code to area withou subregion.

### Retrieve a Code [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

            {"code":
              {
              "uf":"35","nome_uf":"Sao Paulo","mesorregiao_geografica":"3515","nome_mesorregiao":"Metropolitana de Sao Paulo","microrregiao_geografica":"35061","nome_microrregiao":"Sao Paulo","municipio":"50308","nome_municipio":"Sao Paulo","distrito":"01","nome_distrito":"Agua Rasa","subdistrito":"00","nome_subdistrito":""
              }
            }

